Title: Side Quest: Dol Guldur
Text:
The wizard Radagast the Brown asked me to see if all is well in the old fortress of Dol-Guldur.
The green forest is cursed and he thinks there is a source of evil.
I hope he's wrong.
CompleteText:
Here it is, the old fortress of Dol-Guldur.
Radagast was right...a spooky place.
And I feel a dark power.
I should take a look around here.

The air is filled with cold and I feel like I'm being watched..
I wish I had waited for Gandalf..
